great ideas but totally inadequate instruction as a sales pitch for tellington touch , this book is great . as an instruction manual , it is totally worthless . complex gestures such as those mentioned in the book need illustrations that take one step-by-step through the manipulation process . there are n't any , just a few photos that show one stop action part of the whole . it did get me to take a t-touch workshop , which was beneficial for my old and arthritic dog . the process works . the book does n't